The paper discusses agent technology and its application in software engineering, which falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA). The paper also focuses on the design and development of software, which is a key aspect of software engineering (cs.SE). The use of goal-oriented approach and agent designer also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The improvements made to the Goal Net Designer also involve enhancing user friendliness and usability, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
